items.name: ChillDIN-ChillDINGothic
items.description: ChillDIN与寒蝉德黑体。源于德国工业标准字体“DIN”，基于D-DIN的修缮。中文字体的搭配从来源寒蝉端黑体（思源黑体），修改了参数和标点融合。"ChillDIN" is derived from the German industrial standard font 'DIN', based on refinements of D-DIN. The Chinese font pairing originates from ChillDuanSans (Source Han Sans), with modified parameters and integrated punctuation."
